                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elius</ex></expan> Avitianus <lb n="3"/>milis <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> I <expan><abbr>ad</abbr><ex>iutricis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>milit</abbr><ex>avit</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> XI <expan><abbr>vixi</abbr><ex>t</ex></expan> annis <lb n="5"/>XXXI d<expan><ex>e</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>unctus</ex></expan> in Part<expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>ia</abbr></expan> et <expan><abbr>Fla</abbr><ex>via</ex></expan> Gemella <lb n="6"/>mater aeius <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elius</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>Genialis secundus <lb n="8"/><expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>aeres</abbr></expan> <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>aciendum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uravit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes Ädikula mit der Figur eines Soldaten; im Giebelfeld mit Gorgoneion; über den Giebelschrägen Delphine. Z. 2 (Ende) u. 7 (Ende): Buchstabe S steht auf dem Rahmen. Z. 5: DF IN PARTIA wurde nachträglich mit kleineren Buchstaben zwischen Z. 4 u. 5 eingfügt. (B): AE 1909; Mahler; RIU 0720; AE 1995; Ubl: Leseabweichungen.</p>
            </div>
